Standard startup: bbcontroller, logTransmitter, tempReceiver

controller: PID-based temperature controller (requires shunt valve control).
bbcontroller: Simpler On-Off controller.

logTransmitter: Broadcasting log data via UDP.

tempReceiver: Listening for new temperature settings.

weeksetting: Week-based temperature control (nights and weekdays: lower temperatures), warmer in the morning.

remoteTempSetting: Listening on PIO for external temperature control. Switches between two pre-set temperatures. Used instead of tempReceiver.